{
  "stem": "20616.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I said, well, I'm sitting in the last row, but honestly, they moved me into the last-- I was very naive and I thought it was just a natural way I ended up in the last row.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I must say that teacher was very-- was in retrospect, I have respect for the way he handled it, very sensitively.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But later on, he became a terrible-- he reorganized the school, the teachers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Some teachers were fired.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I understand later on, he became director of the school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --that was my experience.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it became- there came a point where my staying-- I wasn't actually thrown out of the school, but there was no point in staying.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Life was made so miserable for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wasn't called on, any kind of class works were either not marked or given back to me with some sort of a stupid remark on it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my father took me out of the school and at that time, a Jewish school was formed just for the purpose of students like us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some sort of a barracks on the outskirts of the city was taken over for that purpose.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was no electricity, no heat when we first started.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was no bell to ring.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember it was a great honor to be made a bell ringer and I was a proud owner of a wrist watch.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And because I had a wrist watch, they made me a bell ringer at one time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] For a while, anyway, till someone else complained and got that honorable job, yeah.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not very long, until our emigration.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Also, my-- my bar mitzvah took place during that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
